Legendary Creature -- Phelddagrif
 {G}: Phelddagrif gains trample until end of
 turn. Target opponent puts a 1/1 green Hippo
 creature token onto the battlefield.

 {W}: Phelddagrif gains flying until end of
 turn. Target opponent gains 2 life.

 {U}: Return Phelddagrif to its owner's hand.
 Target opponent may draw a card.

[gold]                       4/4



